-- Ukrainian troops take southeastern Luhansk, defence minister tells president
-- By Elizabeth Piper
-- Fri Jul 18, 2014 04:15PM EDT
-- None



KIEV, July 18 (Reuters) - Ukraine's defence minister told President Petro Poroshenko on Friday that Ukrainian troops had taken control of the southeastern part of the city of Luhansk in the country's east, a statement on the president's website said.

